abstract: House and Senate Republicans agree on joint budget, first common Congressional spending plan in 10 years; proposed budget would increase military spending and take aim at Pres Obama's signature health care law; deal would also cut education and entitlement programs, like Medicare.
lead_paragraph: The budget would cut education and entitlement programs like Medicare and ease the legislative process to end the Affordable Care Act.
